ProcessRedemption_AaveAdapter_Integration_Concrete_Test
├── when caller not Bob
│  └── it should revert
└── when caller Bob
   ├── given total scaled balance zero
   │  └── it should return zero
   └── given total scaled balance not zero
      ├── given total tokens received zero
      │  └── it should return zero
      └── given total tokens received not zero
         ├── when user token share exceeds share balance
         │  ├── it should return the correct fee amount
         │  ├── it should return the correct amount to transfer to user
         │  └── it should clear the user scaled balance
         └── when user token share not exceed share balance
            ├── it should return correct amount to transfer to user
            ├── it should return zero fee amount
            └── it should clear the user scaled balance
